abstract: Mohaymen wins Fountain of Youth horse race at Gulfstream Park in Hallandale Beach, Fla.

headline.print_headline: Mohaymen Zips to 5-0 in Capturing Fountain
headline.main: Mohaymen Zips to 5-0 in Capturing Fountain

snippet: Mohaymen remained unbeaten by easing to a win in the Grade II, $400,000 Fountain of Youth at Gulfstream Park in Hallandale Beach, Fla.
lead_paragraph: Mohaymen remained unbeaten by easing to a win in the Grade II, $400,000 Fountain of Youth at Gulfstream Park in Hallandale Beach, Fla.
